---
const { name } = Astro.props;
---
<div class="border-2 border-dashed border-red-400 p-6 text-center rounded-xl bg-red-50">
  <p class="text-red-700 font-semibold">
    ⚠️ Neznámy typ bloku: <span class="font-mono">{name}</span>
  </p>
  <p class="text-sm text-red-500 mt-2">
    This block does not yet have a component defined. 
    Add it to <code>src/components</code> and register it in <code>index.astro</code>.
  </p>
</div>
